DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(1,5,1);
$b1 = random(2,7,1);
$c1 = random(-5,-3,1);
$d1 = random(1,2,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Consider the function \( f(x) = $a1 - $b1 x^2, \quad $c1 \leq x \leq $d1 \).
$BR
The absolute maximum value is \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR
EOT
$ans = $a1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and this occurs at \( x \) equals \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR
EOT
$ans = 0;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The absolute minimum value is \{ans_rule(20) \} $BR
EOT
$ans = $a1 - $b1*$c1*$c1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and this occurs at \( x \) equals \{ans_rule(20) \}
EOT
$ans = $c1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
